Q：意大利人不能接受披萨上放菠萝，那中国人有没有类似的饮食禁区？
@此去常风 ：这样大家理解为什么意大利人不能接受披萨放菠萝吗？

 
 
 
Q：如何用一张图劝退想养猫的朋友？
@云中精准辅秾 ：猫和人的其他爱好很多时候是互相冲突的……

 
 
 
Q：如果你有个 1 小时让宠物说话的机会，你会跟它聊什么？
@盖盖子 ：以后别跟仓鼠玩了。 不知道的还以为我养了只咪鼠。

Life on the Amalfi Coast moves to its own rhythm, inviting long lunches, lazy swims and evening aperitivos overlooking some of the most spectacular coastline on Earth. From a homely harbourside B&amp;B to a clifftop converted palazzo, Italy’s most alluring coastline is home to some outstanding accommodation — there’s even a few bargains, if you know where to look.&nbsp;&nbsp;
This article was produced by National Geographic Traveller (UK).
Life on the Amalfi Coast moves to its own rhythm, inviting long lunches, lazy swims and evening aperitivos overlooking some of the most spectacular coastline on Earth. It’s lined with sheer cliffs and pastel-hued villages: Positano, with its steep streets; Amalfi, once the seat of a maritime republic; Ravello, known for its sweeping views …
